294. Memorandum From the Senior Military Assistant (Haig) to the President’s Assistant
                    for National Security Affairs (Kissinger)Source:
                        National Archives, Nixon Presidential
                        Materials, NSC Files, Box 589, Cambodian
                        Operations, Chronology, Vol. II, Nodis/Khmer, through 25 May 1970. Top Secret; Sensitive;
                        Exclusively Eyes Only. May 15 is handwritten on the memorandum.
